## üé® Quick Adjustments

### 1. Overlay Darkness (Most Common)

**Current Code (Line 23):**
```typescript
<div className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50" />
```

**Change the number `/50` to adjust darkness:**

| Value | Darkness | Best For |
|-------|----------|----------|
| `/20` | 20% | Video-focused, minimal text |
| `/30` | 30% | Light overlay, video visible |
| `/40` | 40% | Balanced, good visibility |
| `/50` | 50% | **Current** - Good balance ‚úÖ |
| `/60` | 60% | Text-focused, darker |
| `/70` | 70% | Maximum readability |

**Examples:**
```typescript
// Lighter (video more visible)
<div className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30" />

// Darker (text more readable)
<div className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65" />
```

---

### 2. Video Brightness

**Current Code (Lines 12-20):**
```typescript
<video
  autoPlay
  loop
  muted
  playsInline
  className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
>
```

**Add brightness class:**
```typescript
className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover brightness-110"
```

**Brightness Options:**

| Class | Effect | Use Case |
|-------|--------|----------|
| `brightness-75` | 75% - Darker | Subtle, moody look |
| `brightness-90` | 90% - Slightly dark | Professional, elegant |
| `brightness-100` | 100% - Normal | **Default** ‚úÖ |
| `brightness-110` | 110% - Brighter | Vibrant, energetic |
| `brightness-125` | 125% - Very bright | High-energy, bold |

---

### 3. Video Contrast

**Add contrast to make video sharper or softer:**

```typescript
className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover contrast-110"
```

| Class | Effect | Visual Result |
|-------|--------|---------------|
| `contrast-75` | Low | Soft, muted, subtle |
| `contrast-100` | Normal | **Default** ‚úÖ |
| `contrast-110` | High | Sharp, defined edges |
| `contrast-125` | Very high | Bold, dramatic |

---

### 4. Color Saturation

**Control color intensity:**

```typescript
className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover saturate-110"
```

| Class | Effect | Visual Result |
|-------|--------|---------------|
| `saturate-0` | No color | Black & white |
| `saturate-50` | Low | Muted, desaturated |
| `saturate-100` | Normal | **Default** ‚úÖ |
| `saturate-125` | High | Vibrant, colorful |
| `saturate-150` | Very high | Intense colors |

---

### 5. Blur Effect (Optional)

**Slightly blur video for better text readability:**

```typescript
className="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover blur-sm"
```

| Class | Effect | Use Case |
|-------|--------|----------|
| (none) | No blur | **Default** - Sharp video ‚úÖ |
| `blur-sm` | Slight blur | Subtle, professional |
| `blur-md` | Medium blur | Strong text focus |
| `blur-lg` | Heavy blur | Background effect only |

