## üí° Pro Tips

### Combining Multiple Effects
You can use multiple effects together:

```typescript
className="brightness-110 contrast-105 saturate-110 blur-sm"
```

**Order doesn't matter**, but keep it readable!

### Mobile Considerations
Video might look different on mobile. Test on:
- Desktop (1920px+)
- Tablet (768px-1024px)
- Mobile (375px-768px)

### Performance
- ‚úÖ Single video with effects: Good performance
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Too many heavy effects: May slow down on older devices
- üí° Recommended: Use 2-3 effects maximum

### Accessibility
- Ensure text remains readable
- Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5:1 for body text
- Test with different screen brightness

