## üÜò Troubleshooting

### Video Too Dark
- Decrease overlay: `bg-black/30`
- Increase brightness: `brightness-120`

### Video Too Bright
- Increase overlay: `bg-black/60`
- Decrease brightness: `brightness-85`

### Text Hard to Read
- Increase overlay darkness
- Add slight blur to video
- Increase text shadow (in CSS)

### Video Looks Washed Out
- Increase contrast: `contrast-110`
- Increase saturation: `saturate-110`

### Colors Too Intense
- Decrease saturation: `saturate-75`
- Add slight blur: `blur-sm`

